title: Bollywood celebs mourn 'London thumakda' singer Labh Janjua's demise
text:
Bollywood celebrities like Ayushmann Khurrana, Pritam, Sunidhi Chauhan and Shaan have mourned the tragic demise of Punjabi singer Labh Janjua , calling it a big loss to the Indian music industry.
Janjua, best known for his hit songs like 'London thumakda' and 'Jee karda', was found dead at his residence in Goregaon (West) on ... Â»
